---
title: Butternut Squash and Sage Risotto with Parmesan and Walnuts
description: For us, fall is all about getting our fill of those harvest veggies, and butternut squash is at the top of our list. Its vibrant orange color just screams out to be paired with sweater weather and changing leaves. To up the cozy factor in this perfectly autumnal recipe, we’re embedding it in a warm, creamy risotto and adding fragrant sage and crunchy walnuts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/butternut-squash-and-sage-risotto-df39864b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/butternut-squash-and-sage-risotto-5de6d93ee52f114fe46dbbd2-41343204.pdf
